{"data":[{"id":560533941,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c38f75e73003c034b2f5b1525e1d2738","url_token":"hayashiretsu","name":"医龙烈风","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e2741632528d8f97ae21d9b7e59b4557_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e2741632528d8f97ae21d9b7e59b4557_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c38f75e73003c034b2f5b1525e1d2738","user_type":"people","headline":"热爱解剖的疯子","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":1,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560533941","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545851501,"updated_time":1545851501,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":20,"comment_count":7,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e不请自来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e翻了几个回答就不想再翻了。一是看不懂，二是戾气太重，有些还所问非所答。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e——————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e先说结论：会，而且远不止。不过天才去接受清北高等教育在知识层面上基本没必要了，尤其是去学数学。大神 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/298c7816e6ec5e00fd565672fed0b458\" data-hash=\"298c7816e6ec5e00fd565672fed0b458\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$298c7816e6ec5e00fd565672fed0b458\"\u003e@数学建模老司机\u003c/a\u003e 的回答看起来很靠谱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e——————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e某些“优秀人才”是通过怀疑和蔑视他人收获高高在上的存在感，只能说教育于你而言实为浪费。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不知道的如果想回答直接摆出清北招生办电话让题主自己联系询问就好了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e知道的不是让你来论述猜想多难多不切实际的，你觉得你泼冷水是好心是负责任是忠言逆耳，\u003cb\u003e你算老几？随随便便负责他人的人生？家长和老师会不知道学生现状吗？\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e数学大神真要提出学习建议的，扼要说明必须的最低知识储备，可能的话介绍一些相关书籍和资料就够了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果真的看不懂会知难而退的，其它多余的废话用不着你多说，全世界不是只有你一个人聪明。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e——————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e顺便有人说投机？还是沽名钓誉？可以说非常可笑了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果证不出来钓个毛线的誉哦！你是会安慰人家送人家小花花还是谢谢参与奖状？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果证出来了这点荣誉算毛线哦！你是觉得ta配不上你更聪明更优秀吗，麻烦你去证一个。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"不请自来。翻了几个回答就不想再翻了。一是看不懂，二是戾气太重，有些还所问非所答。——————————先说结论：会，而且远不止。不过天才去接受清北高等教育在知识层面上基本没必要了，尤其是去学数学。大神 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/298c7816e6ec5e00fd565672fed0b458\" data-hash=\"298c7816e6ec5e00fd565672fed0b458\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$298c7816e6ec5e00fd565672fed0b458\"\u003e@数学建模老司机\u003c/a\u003e 的回答看起来很靠谱。—…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=200\u0026p